                    <span>I lost a lot of time reading this poor book and trying to run incomplete  code. The line followed by the author is very confusing. He is always  trying to approach a lot of things at the same time. I think a better help  with working examples would be Java Distributed Objects by Richard Soley. I  would give a zero-star review for this.</span>
                  
